---
import "../styles/global.css";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

const profilePic = import("../assets/galeria/foto.jpg");
---

<div class="bg-amber-400 w-full px-6 md:px-24 py-6 md:py-24" id="brief">
  <div data-aos="fade-up" class="my-6 md:mt-24">
    <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold md:text-7xl lg:text-9xl text-black">
      Sobre mi
    </h3>
  </div>
  <div class="xl:flex xl:flex-row-reverse xl:items-start xl:justify-end">
    <Image
      src={profilePic}
      alt=""
      class:list={[
        "mx-5 w-40 -translate-y-5 h-auto float-right rounded-full sm:w-1/2",
        "xl:mx-0 xl:my-0 xl:float-none xl:w-1/3 xl:ml-12",
        "xl:-translate-y-36 foto",
      ]}
    />

    <div class="mt-8 md:mt-0 space-y-12 w-full lg:w-2/3">
      <p data-aos="fade-up" class="text-black text-sm sm:text-xl xl:text-base">
        Cat ipsum dolor sit amet, lay on arms while you're using the keyboard,
        so cccaaaaaatttssss and howl on top of tall thing. Just going to dip my
        paw in your coffee and do a taste test - oh never mind i forgot i don't
        like coffee - you can have that back now. My slave human didn't give me
        any food so i pooped on the floor there's a forty year old lady there
        let us feast lick butt and make a weird face there's a forty year old
        lady there let us feast, rub whiskers on bare skin act innocent so mewl
        for food at 4am. Sniff other cat's butt and hang jaw half open
        thereafter scratch leg; meow for can opener to feed me, steal mom's
        crouton while she is in the bathroom, or find empty spot in cupboard and
        sleep all day so in the middle of the night i crawl onto your chest and
        purr gently to help you sleep but really likes hummus. I like big cats
        and i can not lie purr when being pet mesmerizing birds but the cat was
        chasing the mouse.
      </p>
      <p data-aos="fade-up" class="text-black text-sm sm:text-xl xl:text-base">
        Play time. Cat slap dog in face swat turds around the house or cat
        snacks. Do doodoo in the litter-box, clickityclack on the piano, be
        frumpygrumpy fight own tail. Love to play with owner's hair tie has
        closed eyes but still sees you for scratch the furniture and meow meow,
        yet ask to go outside and ask to come inside and ask to go outside and
        ask to come inside. Give attitude human give me attention meow get my
        claw stuck in the dog's ear, sleep everywhere, but not in my bed cuddle
        no cuddle cuddle love scratch scratch human clearly uses close to one
        life a night no one naps that long so i revive by standing on
        chestawaken!. Stare at ceiling. Cat snacks sit in window and stare oooh,
        a bird, yum, need to check on human, have not seen in an hour might be
        dead oh look, human is alive, hiss at human, feed me, but gimme
        attention gimme attention gimme attention gimme attention gimme
        attention gimme attention just kidding i don't want it anymore meow bye
        but grass smells good. I shall purr myself to sleep immediately regret
        falling into bathtub sniff other cat's butt and hang jaw half open
        thereafter but chase little red dot someday it will be mine! but
        carrying out surveillance on the neighbour's dog.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>


<style>
  .foto {
    box-shadow: 0rem 0rem 0 1rem rgb(255, 253, 253);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 720px) {
    .foto {
      box-shadow: 1rem -2rem 0 0 rgb(255, 253, 253);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1024px) {
    .foto {
      box-shadow: 1.5rem -1.5rem 0 0 rgb(255, 253, 253);
    }
  }
</style>
